01:39.182 --> 01:42.935
Then I took it out to eat it.

01:45.396 --> 01:46.939
It was...

01:48.566 --> 01:50.067
this big.

01:50.777 --> 01:56.740
Yellow, tasty looking sponge cake.

01:57.200 --> 01:59.451
I held it in my bosom all day.

02:01.579 --> 02:06.250
Then I saw a girl carrying
her sister on her back.

02:07.085 --> 02:09.544
Looked obvious
they were starving.

02:10.463 --> 02:16.718
So pale, weak and helpless

02:18.096 --> 02:21.181
I turned away to eat it.

02:21.182 --> 02:26.937
But I ended up giving it to them.

02:28.481 --> 02:32.276
It must've been warm since

02:32.694 --> 02:35.904
I carried it around all day.

02:38.283 --> 02:44.538
I didn't know if I'll ever
have cake like that again.

02:48.585 --> 02:53.463
She gobbled it down and shoved
some in her sisters mouth.

02:54.883 --> 02:58.552
Think God will remember that?

02:58.595 --> 03:00.470
Though its been 30 years?

03:03.224 --> 03:04.474
Absoposilutely.

03:05.059 --> 03:06.810
Remembering is His specialty.

03:07.854 --> 03:09.021
Of course.

03:09.772 --> 03:18.530
That song, Father Can you
play it for me, again?

03:44.265 --> 03:46.099
You can do CPR, right?

03:49.687 --> 03:50.646
Go!

03:53.191 --> 03:54.107
Stop!

03:57.570 --> 03:58.528
Again!

04:10.708 --> 04:11.667
200 Joules.

04:24.055 --> 04:25.013
Charge.

04:28.309 --> 04:31.561
Those who seek direct communication
with God are prone to self-hatred...

04:31.562 --> 04:36.858
The Devil will eat right into you.

04:36.859 --> 04:40.279
As St. Bruno said, 'Suicide
is to die a martyr for Satan.'

04:41.322 --> 04:44.283
It's worse than first degree murder.

04:44.867 --> 04:46.827
It's worth a life sentence...
in hell.

04:49.872 --> 04:52.249
20 Hail Mary's, get
lots of sun

04:52.292 --> 04:53.834
and take a cold shower.

04:54.043 --> 05:00.465
Get Gods help through science
and take some anti-depressants

05:02.677 --> 05:04.136
Stop thinking about
killing yourself.

05:04.137 --> 05:08.265
And... forget the
bastard who dumped you.

05:15.690 --> 05:16.857
Father...

05:18.067 --> 05:21.111
Ill deal with the bastards
and the worldly matters.

05:22.488 --> 05:24.614
You just stick to praying, Father.

05:25.867 --> 05:29.536
Ask the bishop to send
me to Emmanuel Labs, please?

05:31.039 --> 05:36.043
The Vatican does not
approve ofthat experiment.

05:37.587 --> 05:41.757
Sarah died on Monday
even after 8 surgeries.

05:42.300 --> 05:44.634
Hyo-sung went into
a coma yesterday.

05:46.179 --> 05:49.389
It kills me to watch them dying.

05:50.058 --> 05:55.187
No one knows what
really goes on at that lab.

05:57.065 --> 05:59.358
I want to save people.

06:01.861 --> 06:05.197
I told you to go to med school
since you were in the crib,

06:05.239 --> 06:08.533
study ophthalmology,
and heal my eyes.

06:08.576 --> 06:11.203
But Father, I must go and...

06:11.245 --> 06:14.122
Enough! I'll just give you absolution.

06:17.877 --> 06:20.462
Stick to the confession!
Geeze!

06:24.092 --> 06:27.552
Dear patients, I regret not
seeing you before I left.

06:28.763 --> 06:31.431
I was busy preparing
for my sudden vacation.

06:33.393 --> 06:35.644
I packed a bunch ofthings.

06:36.479 --> 06:38.230
But they say to bring my body only.

06:38.231 --> 06:42.234
The monastery prepared a
luxurious hotel for me.

06:42.235 --> 06:45.112
Fr. Emmanuel Memorial
Biochemical Labs
At times like this
I'm glad I joined The Order.

08:58.246 --> 09:02.123
Grant me the following in the name
of our Lord Jesus Christ

09:03.376 --> 09:06.753
Like a leper rotting in flesh,
let all avoid me.

09:07.880 --> 09:12.133
Like a cripple without limbs,
let me not move freely.

09:14.136 --> 09:17.722
Remove my cheeks,
that tears may not roll down them.

09:18.683 --> 09:22.727
Crush my lips and tongue,
that I may not sin with them.

09:23.062 --> 09:26.565
Pull out my nails
that I may grasp nothing.

09:26.607 --> 09:30.235
Let my shoulders and back be bent
that I may carry nothing.

09:32.780 --> 09:36.575
Like a man with tumor in the head
let me lackjudgment.

09:38.077 --> 09:42.038
Ravage my body sworn to chastity
leave me with no pride,

09:42.081 --> 09:44.165
and have me live in shame.

09:45.376 --> 09:47.544
Let no one pray for me.

09:47.587 --> 09:51.923
But only the grace ofthe Lord
Jesus Christ have mercy on me.

10:01.058 --> 10:02.767
A month has gone by already.

10:03.603 --> 10:08.440
Watching the grand view through
the window is more fun than TV.

10:10.276 --> 10:12.068
The hotel owner gave me
her best room,

10:12.069 --> 10:14.446
saying I'm handsome.

10:15.698 --> 10:19.326
Thanks to all the sunlight
my skin is tanned and peeling.

12:06.976 --> 12:09.853
Time of death, 3:31 p.m.

12:21.907 --> 12:23.241
Grant me the following

12:23.284 --> 12:26.161
in the name of
our Lord Jesus Christ.

12:27.288 --> 12:30.957
Like a leper rotting in flesh,
let all avoid me.

12:31.917 --> 12:33.042
Like a cripple without limbs...

12:33.043 --> 12:35.211
His skin...

12:37.173 --> 12:38.590
let me not move freely...

12:40.801 --> 12:42.594
6 months later

12:54.815 --> 12:56.608
Touch my leg, Father!

12:56.650 --> 12:59.611
Please pray for me, Father!

12:59.653 --> 13:01.237
Please, Father?

13:02.072 --> 13:05.074
My daughter has leukemia!

13:19.089 --> 13:21.341
You know how much he talked

13:21.884 --> 13:24.135
Saying the pain is killing him,

13:24.178 --> 13:27.347
but still on and on about
the sponge cakes, this and that.

13:27.389 --> 13:28.348
That very day,

13:29.642 --> 13:34.145
I was about to doze off after a long
night shift when I was paged.

13:34.814 --> 13:36.272
A thought crossed my mind.

13:37.817 --> 13:41.528
What if I walked a little slowly,
just a little.

13:42.279 --> 13:45.240
If he passed away now, he'd only be
two months earlier than expected.

13:46.867 --> 13:50.537
I thought my life would be a lot
more bearable without him.

13:50.538 --> 13:53.414
By the time I arrived
on dragging feet

13:54.875 --> 14:00.129
hypoxia had lead to a brain damage
and he had already gone quiet.

14:02.174 --> 14:03.883
He's been in that state for a year now.

14:05.386 --> 14:07.053
He's still my patient, and.. .

14:09.098 --> 14:11.558
every time I see him, I feel.. .

14:11.559 --> 14:14.686
You feel terrible about it?

14:14.728 --> 14:18.314
Not... terrible,

14:19.275 --> 14:20.942
but uncomfortable.

14:21.735 --> 14:24.863
Thought I'd let him go two months earlier
and he's still around after a year.

14:26.282 --> 14:29.242
It's a miracle that he is still alive.

14:30.077 --> 14:33.872
They say it's thanks to your prayers.

14:41.922 --> 14:44.048
Dermatologists would be
happy to see this.

14:45.092 --> 14:50.138
All the numbers indicate
you're healing up incredibly fast.

14:51.056 --> 14:52.849
What's it like, being a man of miracle?

14:54.727 --> 14:57.729
I've become strangely sensitive
to sound and smell.

14:57.730 --> 15:00.732
It makes me feel dizzy and nauseous.

15:00.733 --> 15:03.943
The symptoms aren't related to EV,

15:05.362 --> 15:07.071
but more like a pregnancy.

15:18.918 --> 15:20.501
I heard...

15:21.754 --> 15:26.507
people are coming to seek prayers
from The Bandaged Saint?

15:27.384 --> 15:29.719
Don't know how that
nonsense started.

15:35.184 --> 15:37.518
Though I did hear
of some people getting cured.

15:39.563 --> 15:42.148
Guess it can have
a psychological effect.

15:43.567 --> 15:47.362
After all, you're the only one
who survived out of 50 volunteers.

15:49.782 --> 15:50.740
Right?

15:53.535 --> 15:58.247
Wow! You're so lucky!

16:14.181 --> 16:17.558
Are you the miracle
survivor out of 500?

16:18.268 --> 16:21.437
My son has cancer!

16:22.481 --> 16:25.066
Please pray for him!

16:26.986 --> 16:31.030
It's just a psychological effect
Theres nothing I can do.

16:35.828 --> 16:36.828
Look.

16:48.590 --> 16:50.049
Channel 9 won't come on, Mom.

16:50.092 --> 16:51.342
Let's pray kids.

16:57.391 --> 17:01.519
Did you ever live in Busan?

17:04.356 --> 17:08.608
We are gathered here
to pray for Kang-woo.

17:10.069 --> 17:12.530
Born under Your grace and love,

17:13.656 --> 17:16.909
embracing even
a wounded street dog...

17:18.078 --> 17:20.538
he was a kind hearted boy.

17:21.290 --> 17:23.624
Remember his goodness
and have mercy on him.

17:24.585 --> 17:27.545
In Jesus' name we pray.

17:27.588 --> 17:28.629
- Amen.
- Amen.

17:31.008 --> 17:37.805
I don't believe in this
but since it's from an old friend...

17:42.853 --> 17:44.645
Now, I recognize you, son.

17:45.481 --> 17:47.231
Sorry. You're a Father, now.

17:49.860 --> 17:51.652
Im sorry, Father.

17:54.948 --> 17:58.076
You used to come over
for noodles.

17:58.118 --> 18:02.371
Fifth grade, right?
You lived at the church orphanage?

18:03.791 --> 18:05.666
My son could never pass stray

18:05.667 --> 18:09.337
cats and was so good
to the orphans.

18:09.755 --> 18:12.924
Your sister was so shy and
ran out whenever I came over.

18:14.551 --> 18:19.138
She had calluses on her feet
and Kang-woo made me touch them.

18:23.936 --> 18:27.355
Her parents rented
a small room in our house.

18:28.941 --> 18:32.443
Her father was
a high school drop out.

18:32.945 --> 18:37.949
This is my blood shed for
you so that sins may be forgiven.

18:38.200 --> 18:43.538
One day, they left her in my room
and said they'd be back soon.

18:44.289 --> 18:45.915
But they never came back!

18:46.959 --> 18:49.710
So I took the three-year-old

18:49.753 --> 18:52.713
in and raised her
like a daughter and puppy.

18:53.173 --> 18:55.550
Happy Hanbok
Shed call me 'mommy'

18:55.968 --> 18:57.844
I'm her mommy-in-law, now.

19:01.390 --> 19:03.641
Marriage was no big deal.

19:04.184 --> 19:07.854
She just moved from sleeping
in my bed to Kang-woo's.

19:11.108 --> 19:15.820
Why'd you buy the laver
at that place again, Mom?

19:16.864 --> 19:24.453
I told you it's no good and
the owner's a cocksucker

19:55.777 --> 19:57.153
You hate Kimbap?

19:58.197 --> 20:01.657
No, I'm sensitive to smell
these days.

20:02.367 --> 20:05.036
I suddenly got a whiff of blood.

20:09.666 --> 20:11.042
Kang-woos home.

20:12.211 --> 20:14.253
- Mom, I caught a cold!
- What?

20:14.296 --> 20:15.671
Hi, Sang-hyun!

20:15.672 --> 20:17.757
I told you
to wear your long johns.

20:17.799 --> 20:20.635
- Were here, too
- Welcome.

20:21.762 --> 20:23.012
My friend the priest.

20:23.555 --> 20:26.265
This is our dam's
manager and his wife.

20:26.266 --> 20:29.727
It's an honor, Father
I'm Young-du

20:29.770 --> 20:32.647
She's a Filipina
so she's Catholic.

20:32.689 --> 20:34.732
Say hello, Evelyn.

20:43.200 --> 20:47.036
- Tae-ju!
- How've you been?

20:53.293 --> 20:56.337
Here comes the Police Chief!

20:56.672 --> 21:01.717
Please, I quit
the force a long time ago.

21:03.136 --> 21:05.638
He's the dam's security
head This is Fr. Hyun, Sang-hyun

21:05.681 --> 21:06.722
Hello.

21:06.765 --> 21:08.349
Do you like fishing Father?

21:08.392 --> 21:13.020
Get on his good side and you
can fish there though its banned.

21:13.063 --> 21:15.731
Daytimes a bit tricky.
Come by at nights.

21:15.774 --> 21:18.859
- Have a seat, Father
- Let's get started.

21:23.490 --> 21:27.910
Koreans don't
appreciate Mahjong.

21:29.955 --> 21:33.124
Would you like to play, Father?

21:33.125 --> 21:36.127
- Sorry. I don't know how
- I see.

21:38.130 --> 21:42.008
Did I tell you about Father Hyun
praying for Kang-woo?

21:43.969 --> 21:47.471
I was standing right
next to my son.

21:47.889 --> 21:52.852
Suddenly, I felt something hot
come down on my head.

21:52.894 --> 21:59.150
I felt tingly all over like
someone was poking me with needles.

22:02.362 --> 22:07.450
Then my boy said
'It feels hot right here, Mom.'

22:10.662 --> 22:13.039
Then the cancer vanished.

22:13.582 --> 22:14.832
It vanished?

22:17.502 --> 22:20.129
You always feel tingly
cuz of your blood pressure.

22:20.172 --> 22:22.757
But I did a biopsyjust in case.

22:25.177 --> 22:29.764
The endoscope showed
it was esophagus cancer.

22:30.390 --> 22:33.100
Women shouldn't
get sedated endoscopes.

22:33.560 --> 22:37.813
Doctors secretly rape them.

22:44.488 --> 22:45.654
I win!

22:46.948 --> 22:49.950
Three closed triplets!

22:50.410 --> 22:51.952
That's 8 points.

22:55.957 --> 22:59.835
Can we turn the heater down?

23:00.587 --> 23:01.545
But I'm cold.

23:04.174 --> 23:05.466
Kang-woo says he's cold!

23:06.760 --> 23:09.929
Thank you very much.

23:36.873 --> 23:38.666
I'm losing so much.

23:39.418 --> 23:41.836
Instead ofthe hot water bag!

24:14.870 --> 24:16.829
I'm going down to get
the lights in the store.

25:29.152 --> 25:30.945
Don't you love our Mahjong gang?

25:35.992 --> 25:38.244
Wednesdays. Mercury. Water.

25:38.245 --> 25:40.829
Oasis! How's that
for our gang's name?

28:46.766 --> 28:49.017
She's a Catholic Veronica.

28:50.270 --> 28:52.229
She was in a bad hit-and-run.

28:54.357 --> 28:56.150
Lost a lot of blood.

28:56.568 --> 28:58.235
She doesn't have much time.

29:03.783 --> 29:05.868
Let this water call to mind
your baptismal sharing...

29:05.910 --> 29:10.038
in Christ's redeeming
passion and resurrection.

29:11.708 --> 29:14.835
Veronica. Make your confession.

29:36.483 --> 29:41.612
By the power the apostolic See
has given me in the name ofthe...

29:41.654 --> 29:43.530
Father, the Son,
and the Holy Spirit, I grant you

29:43.573 --> 29:44.615
a plenary indulgence and...

29:50.163 --> 29:52.122
pardon for all your sins.

29:52.165 --> 29:53.123
Amen.

29:57.086 --> 29:59.630
Through this holy anointing...

30:01.966 --> 30:04.134
may the Lord in his
love and mercy help you...

30:06.638 --> 30:09.973
with the grace ofthe Holy Spirit.

30:12.560 --> 30:13.644
And...

30:14.813 --> 30:17.272
may the Lord who
frees you from sin...

30:18.191 --> 30:22.236
save you and raise you up.

30:24.364 --> 30:25.239
Amen.

34:22.768 --> 34:24.728
Where'd you wander
offto this time?

34:26.856 --> 34:29.815
I woke up I was at the pharmacy.

34:29.859 --> 34:31.902
And some man walked past.

34:32.862 --> 34:35.155
Aren't there pills
for sleepwalking?

34:36.491 --> 34:39.159
I should lock your room
from the outside.

34:39.202 --> 34:40.911
Should've got me pills
for my cold.

34:42.789 --> 34:43.830
Weren't you cold?

34:44.498 --> 34:46.166
You never catch a cold.

34:49.670 --> 34:51.254
She's a Yeti, Mom.

35:00.848 --> 35:02.808
Smells like
when you had gastritis.

35:03.267 --> 35:05.143
I'll go find the pills.

35:08.189 --> 35:10.357
Must you do this to believe me?

35:14.403 --> 35:17.280
Don't grab my heart so hard.

35:33.965 --> 35:36.842
When I drank Hyo-sung's blood...

35:37.176 --> 35:38.718
the blisters disappeared.

35:39.595 --> 35:41.930
It's as ifthe vampire cells
suppressed EV.

35:43.850 --> 35:45.851
But, it doesn't last very long.

35:48.104 --> 35:49.020
Father...

35:49.856 --> 35:52.649
I didn't choose the blood
that was transfused into me!

35:53.943 --> 35:56.236
You know I went
there to do good!

36:01.868 --> 36:04.619
Now, I thirst after
all sinful pleasures.

36:05.746 --> 36:09.541
But how can I get human
blood without killing!

36:10.209 --> 36:11.168
First...

36:12.044 --> 36:15.005
The Lord said not to worry
about what to eat.

36:15.464 --> 36:17.632
For He feeds even
whe birds in the sky.

36:18.301 --> 36:19.259
Here.

36:39.030 --> 36:40.155
I think I won.

36:41.365 --> 36:43.658
Small four winds!

36:44.285 --> 36:46.536
Closed, halfflush,
bonus 3 points!

36:47.872 --> 36:49.831
30 bucks! You lose!

36:52.960 --> 36:56.546
Some priest.
From Macao or something?

36:56.881 --> 37:02.344
He's the only one
who survived out of 500.

37:02.553 --> 37:04.262
500, yeah right.

37:41.467 --> 37:42.842
When did you go out?

37:43.761 --> 37:45.637
I didn't see you.

38:34.895 --> 38:38.648
It's ah...
kind of an infectious disease.

38:40.151 --> 38:41.109
Scary, isn't it?

38:42.028 --> 38:45.030
How different...
without his glasses.

38:47.783 --> 38:49.451
How can you get infected?

38:51.787 --> 38:54.456
Not through a kiss for sure.

38:54.957 --> 38:57.751
I never kissed
anyone in my life.

39:02.298 --> 39:03.381
Until now.

39:32.244 --> 39:34.662
I don't get shy.

39:36.665 --> 39:38.750
I didn't run out cuz I'm shy.

39:40.086 --> 39:42.962
Back in Busan...

39:44.256 --> 39:46.424
It's cuz I was
sick of everything.

39:51.764 --> 39:56.351
The mom, idiot son,
and the dark, damp house.

39:56.852 --> 39:59.562
The non-stop weepy, old songs.

40:06.695 --> 40:08.738
I waited for you to come.

40:09.782 --> 40:11.950
The orphanage boy...

40:14.245 --> 40:15.870
I waited for you...

40:16.872 --> 40:18.373
when I was young...

40:20.584 --> 40:22.544
cuz the idiot liked you.

40:23.671 --> 40:25.839
When you came,
he left me alone.

40:33.681 --> 40:36.015
I'm not a shy person.

40:49.905 --> 40:51.865
I run out on my bare feet...

40:52.783 --> 40:55.743
to escape from
this hell sooner.

41:05.254 --> 41:07.297
I even run out from my sleep.

41:07.756 --> 41:09.841
They think its sleepwalking.

41:10.259 --> 41:14.471
I feel awake only then
and asleep the rest ofthe time.

42:37.429 --> 42:38.638
Honey!

42:40.349 --> 42:41.391
Tae-ju!

42:41.684 --> 42:42.725
Hot water bag!

42:43.978 --> 42:44.936
Tae-ju?

42:47.147 --> 42:48.398
Tae-ju!

43:21.765 --> 43:23.057
You bitch!

43:23.684 --> 43:25.768
There she goes again.

43:25.769 --> 43:27.645
I fed you and raised you!

43:27.688 --> 43:30.440
Go put her to bed!

43:31.442 --> 43:34.652
You can't even change
your husband's hot water bag?

43:34.695 --> 43:37.864
How dare you!

43:38.282 --> 43:39.324
I win.

43:39.617 --> 43:40.658
Let go!

43:46.165 --> 43:49.834
Stomach troubles?
What took you so long?

43:49.877 --> 43:52.420
Eat up other's money
and you'll get diarrhea.

44:02.598 --> 44:03.514
What's got into you?

44:05.476 --> 44:07.060
This looks fun.

44:08.187 --> 44:10.146
So exciting to touch.

44:12.483 --> 44:14.317
I could do it all night, too.

44:14.360 --> 44:15.943
You don't even know
how to do it.

44:17.237 --> 44:18.321
Me?

44:19.448 --> 44:21.032
I know how to do it.

44:22.159 --> 44:23.326
I'm good.

44:25.788 --> 44:28.498
They are on fire!

44:29.541 --> 44:33.044
I can't wait till next Wednesday.

44:33.087 --> 44:35.338
Then how about Sundays, too?

44:36.715 --> 44:37.757
Why not?

44:38.967 --> 44:39.967
Well...

44:42.179 --> 44:44.972
It's Easter Sunday
I'm staying at the hospital.

44:45.974 --> 44:48.935
It's best to leave things
in wanting.

44:50.771 --> 44:52.313
Did you touch her?

44:53.524 --> 44:55.650
I kissed her and held her.

44:57.986 --> 44:59.237
Undress her?

45:03.075 --> 45:04.951
Not completely.

45:06.161 --> 45:09.163
The Good Book says to
cut offthe hand that sins.. .

45:10.290 --> 45:13.167
but no matter how many times I do.. .
I can't control my heart.

45:14.795 --> 45:15.753
Mom...

45:18.799 --> 45:19.757
I...

45:21.969 --> 45:24.595
can't live like this anymore.

45:26.056 --> 45:27.306
I...

45:29.351 --> 45:32.603
I want to help the needy.

45:36.567 --> 45:40.027
Maybe I can volunteer
at a hospital or something.

