02:01:40.459 --> 02:01:42.460
- 'K'!
- 'K'?

02:01:43.963 --> 02:01:45.463
L. D. K?

02:01:54.056 --> 02:01:57.851
Ladies Delaying,
Killing the game.

02:01:59.395 --> 02:02:02.022
'D' comes last! 'KLD'!

02:02:02.023 --> 02:02:04.107
Mrs. Ra, it's 'DKL', right?

02:02:07.862 --> 02:02:09.821
