02:02:09.864 --> 02:02:13.908
'KLD'? 'KILLED'?

02:02:15.578 --> 02:02:16.619
I'm right?

02:02:18.664 --> 02:02:21.833
See? It's 'KILLED'!

02:02:23.878 --> 02:02:25.754
Whatever, let's keep
the game alive.

02:02:27.173 --> 02:02:31.926
